        <div class="w-14 relative">
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -left-36 top-55 rotate-90 inline-block text-stone-500 text-base/4 text-display whitespace-pre-line">
            ISO 3533 COMPLIANT INFORMATION SYSTEM
